description.en:
100% of the profits generated from the sale of the Saint Fame Face Mask will be donated to Red Cross in Crypto to support those impacted by COVID-19.

The $ICK Mask is a face mask by Saint Fame, the world's first internet-owned fashion house. It is the first piece collectively designed by the disciples of Saint Fame.

Purchasing exactly 1 $ICK will entitle you to one real face mask, shipped anywhere in the world.
